# Cloudflare Pages — cấu hình routing (SPA fallback + proxy sitemap).
# Proxy sitemap cho Googlebot sang backend Render — giữ nguyên URL public (không có prefix /api/v1).
/sitemap_index.xml  https://webchoviet-server.onrender.com/sitemap_index.xml  200
/sitemaps/*         https://webchoviet-server.onrender.com/sitemaps/:splat    200

# SPA fallback — mọi route con (React Router) đều render qua index.html.
/*                  /index.html                                              200
